beer.beer_description:
Cacao / Vanilla

We told you to be good and "Eat Your Greens" so now you are allowed dessert and what’s a birthday without cake? So we have made a liquid cake with a very sensible serving suggestion...in your mouth!

Open wide for an imperial stout loaded with the chocolatey goodness of cacao and lashings of vanilla. We are really happy with where our stouts are sitting at the moment. We have explored coffee, maple syrup, smoke, salted caramel and now cacao and vanilla. More stout adventures to come throughout the year!

items.badge_description: Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 265 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 54!

At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 100 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 21! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

Porters and Stouts are rich with both history and flavor. Roasty, dark, and delicious, these two styles helped start it all. That’s 35 different beers with the style of Porter or Stout. Try 5 more for Level 8!
